Release 0.5-pre1:

	* bigarray support in sdlvideo module
	* SDL-1.2, SDL_image-1.2.0, SDL_mixer-1.2.0, SDL_ttf-1.2.2 support
	  but not fully  implemented.
	* major changes in the internal structure of directories
	* some bugfixes 
	* works with ocaml-3.01

